{"tid":957184,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇睇爬蟲（鬆獅）獸醫推介？","createTime":"2018-12-26T23:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T06:16:26.000Z","uid":122987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c989fcc12a8a6eba5c50b04833348f13683c6ee6","tid":957184,"uid":122987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T23:22:26.000Z","msg":"我隻鬆獅無咩精神 唔食野 <br />\n想帶佢睇下獸醫睇下係咪生積<br />\n有冇巴絲有推介 <br />\n但上網睇過大圍珍禽口碑麻麻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134bf70d97a27e713f927fce4fe6262e2694d054","tid":957184,"uid":99607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:44:35.000Z","msg":"靠自己經驗好過去睇獸醫啦<br />\n你個環境係點 有無裝暖管<br />\n餵開咩"},{"pid":"884624e1b0a0cf54c99af77bcbe865fd2ff56485","tid":957184,"uid":59675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T03:51:21.000Z","msg":"睇荃灣享和珍禽異獸醫療中心, 楊醫生同孫醫生都好細心<br />\n<br />\n不過睇之前您隻鬆獅係唔係突然凍左先咁? <br />\n可能係好小事過兩日暖返就冇事"},{"pid":"ee17eac681fdd84faff1a3193f9b8480257010c0","tid":957184,"uid":169419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"荃灣享和珍禽異獸 楊醫生 好nice好有耐性<br />\n你有冇帶鬆去杜過蟲？<br />\n或者睇下係咪唔夠暖？<br />\n我隻鬆前排一樣都係食欲不振 過左幾日就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}